org.openhubframework.openhub.api.event

Annotation Type EventNotifier


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Documented
@Component
public @interface EventNotifier
    Indicates that an annotated class is a Camel EventNotifier event notifier class. This class is also marked as Spring bean and will be automatically registered into Camel context.
    Author:
    Petr Juza
